1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<b><font color="#7b8184"><font size="30">Advanced Class</font></font></b></font>

2
00:00:01,730 --> 00:00:03,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<font size="10"><font face="Arial"><font color="#b8c7b3"><b>Jan. 14th (Tues.)
 Class Duty: Minazuki</b></font></font></font></font>

3
00:00:02,120 --> 00:00:06,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isaki and I are thinking 
of becoming two separate humans.</font>

4
00:00:07,410 --> 00:00:09,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Separate humans?</font>

5
00:00:09,420 --> 00:00:10,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

6
00:00:10,650 --> 00:00:13,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At first, the plan was 
to become one human,</font>

7
00:00:13,300 --> 00:00:17,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to stop living a halfhearted 
existence as a werewolf...</font>

8
00:00:18,060 --> 00:00:20,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But after talking things over,</font>

9
00:00:21,220 --> 00:00:25,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we don't see a need to merge 
into a single personality.</font>

10
00:00:26,020 --> 00:00:29,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does that mean you'll 
each have your own body?</font>

11
00:00:29,140 --> 00:00:30,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

12
00:00:30,050 --> 00:00:32,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that even possible?!</font>

13
00:00:32,340 --> 00:00:37,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When we enrolled, the director 
told us that was an option.</font>

14
00:00:38,070 --> 00:00:39,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

15
00:00:39,640 --> 00:00:44,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I used to think it'd be better 
if I didn't exist.</font>

16
00:00:44,650 --> 00:00:46,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But after starting 
an exchange diary with Isaki,</font>

17
00:00:46,830 --> 00:00:48,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we want to be there for each other.</font>

18
00:00:49,570 --> 00:00:50,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

19
00:00:50,860 --> 00:00:54,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure, I'll discuss it 
with the principal and director.</font>

20
00:00:55,580 --> 00:00:56,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much!</font>

21
00:00:57,150 --> 00:01:00,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So what will you do 
after you become humans?</font>

22
00:01:00,390 --> 00:01:04,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Until now, you were planning to enter 
a private liberal arts university.</font>

23
00:01:04,530 --> 00:01:07,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But now with two Ohgamis 
in need of a career path...</font>

24
00:01:07,230 --> 00:01:08,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

25
00:01:08,240 --> 00:01:09,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eh?</font>

26
00:01:10,220 --> 00:01:11,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no, Mr. Hitoma.</font>

27
00:01:12,410 --> 00:01:15,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't think about that at all!</font>

28
00:01:16,130 --> 00:01:16,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah...</font>

29
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:53,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="14"><font color="#f5f5f5">Episode <font size="21">6</font></font></font></font></font>

30
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:53,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="14"><font color="#f5f5f5">Episode <font size="21">6</font></font></font></font></font>

31
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:53,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="13"><font color="#effefb">The Misanthrope and the Light of Dawn</font></font></font></font>

32
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:53,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="13"><font color="#effefb">The Misanthrope and the Light of Dawn</font></font></font></font>

33
00:02:50,020 --> 00:02:51,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<font size="24"><font face="Arial"><font color="#edf4f5">Jan. 17th (Fri.)
Class Duty: Usami</font></font></font></font>

34
00:02:50,940 --> 00:02:51,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Okay,</font>

35
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:54,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}let's talk about the final
assignments for the advanced class.</font>

36
00:02:55,690 --> 00:03:00,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In order to graduate and become human, 
you need to pass the final assignment.</font>

37
00:03:01,220 --> 00:03:05,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The principal and director will prepare 
a personalized task for each of you.</font>

38
00:03:05,900 --> 00:03:07,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">None of that matters to me.</font>

39
00:03:08,390 --> 00:03:12,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I got 150 points deducted 
for sneaking off campus.</font>

40
00:03:12,420 --> 00:03:15,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So there's no point in doing 
the final assignment.</font>

41
00:03:15,630 --> 00:03:18,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"The final assignment</font>

42
00:03:18,030 --> 00:03:22,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is meant to challenge you
in ways that a class can't teach."</font>

43
00:03:23,140 --> 00:03:25,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or so the principal said.</font>

44
00:03:26,900 --> 00:03:30,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Graduation or not, 
you'll have to do the assignment.</font>

45
00:03:30,460 --> 00:03:32,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have until the end 
of February to submit it.</font>

46
00:03:32,830 --> 00:03:35,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want you all to do 
your best to complete it.</font>

47
00:03:41,160 --> 00:03:45,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've just received our final 
assignments from the principal.</font>

48
00:03:45,350 --> 00:03:50,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mine is to hunt down 
one of the director's gems.</font>

49
00:03:50,060 --> 00:03:51,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A treasure hunt?</font>

50
00:03:51,500 --> 00:03:54,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This contains hints to the gem's location.</font>

51
00:03:52,770 --> 00:03:58,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#fbfeff"><font face="Arial"><font size="22">Final Assignment
 <font color="#aaa9a3">Kyoka Minazuki</font></font></font></font></font>

52
00:03:54,410 --> 00:03:57,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? Now that sounds like a fun time.</font>

53
00:03:58,650 --> 00:04:00,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As for me,</font>

54
00:04:00,340 --> 00:04:04,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have to collect the signatures of 
every enrolled student and faculty member.</font>

55
00:04:04,230 --> 00:04:05,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Signatures?</font>

56
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:07,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So they just write down their names?</font>

57
00:04:07,300 --> 00:04:08,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're treating me like I'm stupid.</font>

58
00:04:08,810 --> 00:04:10,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This should be easy.</font>

59
00:04:10,020 --> 00:04:15,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mine is writing the sports anthem 
for our field day next year.</font>

60
00:04:15,700 --> 00:04:18,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sounds perfect 
for a music lover like you.</font>

61
00:04:18,620 --> 00:04:26,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have to write a 20,000-character novella
with a cast of five or more people.</font>

62
00:04:28,110 --> 00:04:31,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>None of the assignments 
seem overly difficult.</i></font>

63
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:37,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Instead of the end of February, 
we might see everyone finish in January.</i></font>

64
00:04:38,520 --> 00:04:42,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<font size="24"><font face="Arial"><font color="#edf4f5"><font size="20">Jan. 24th (Fri.)
Class Duty: Minazuki</font></font></font></font></font>

65
00:04:39,490 --> 00:04:42,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How are you all doing 
on your final assignments?</font>

66
00:04:43,130 --> 00:04:45,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pretty good, if you ask me.</font>

67
00:04:45,050 --> 00:04:47,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm done with the melody 
and the lyrics for the chorus.</font>

68
00:04:47,590 --> 00:04:50,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're working on the lyrics 
and music at the same time?</font>

69
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:53,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted to nail the chorus first 
since it's the key part,</font>

70
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:56,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and then build out the rest from there.</font>

71
00:04:56,670 --> 00:04:59,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh, now that's an interesting approach.</font>

72
00:04:59,890 --> 00:05:01,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about you, Usami?</font>

73
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:04,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've already talked to every student.</font>

74
00:05:04,280 --> 00:05:05,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's impossible.</font>

75
00:05:05,810 --> 00:05:07,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean?</font>

76
00:05:07,940 --> 00:05:08,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take a look.</font>

77
00:05:09,370 --> 00:05:11,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are these... paw prints?</font>

78
00:05:12,410 --> 00:05:16,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The beginner class is still getting 
used to their human forms,</font>

79
00:05:16,530 --> 00:05:18,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and a lot of the students can't write yet.</font>

80
00:05:18,930 --> 00:05:23,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I got their paw prints, but the principal
said they don't count as signatures.</font>

81
00:05:23,910 --> 00:05:26,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The beginner class won't be easy...</font>

82
00:05:27,430 --> 00:05:29,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How are you doing, Ohgami?</font>

83
00:05:30,780 --> 00:05:33,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why would they say this?</font>

84
00:05:33,140 --> 00:05:36,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why? I can't understand how they feel!</font>

85
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:39,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sounds like you're struggling, too.</font>

86
00:05:39,590 --> 00:05:41,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How's your assignment going, Minazuki?</font>

87
00:05:41,440 --> 00:05:46,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The first hint was a crossword puzzle, 
which I found hard but managed to solve.</font>

88
00:05:46,790 --> 00:05:47,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

89
00:05:47,910 --> 00:05:51,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The next one's just as difficult, 
and I'm still figuring it out.</font>

90
00:05:51,570 --> 00:05:53,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure I'll manage to get it, though!</font>

91
00:05:53,830 --> 00:05:55,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since I solved the first one.</font>

92
00:05:56,380 --> 00:05:57,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

93
00:05:58,980 --> 00:06:00,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's still more than a month left.</font>

94
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:02,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't stress out and panic.</font>

95
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:05,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just keep on chipping away. Got it?</font>

96
00:06:05,790 --> 00:06:06,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

97
00:06:07,110 --> 00:06:09,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<font size="20"><b><font face="Arial"><font color="#edf4f5">Jan. 31st (Fri.)
Class Duty: Ohgami</font></font></b></font></font>

98
00:06:08,030 --> 00:06:09,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There we go!</font>

99
00:06:09,700 --> 00:06:12,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Music and lyrics, all done!</font>

100
00:06:12,850 --> 00:06:15,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad to hear it, Haneda.</font>

101
00:06:15,780 --> 00:06:20,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once I show it to the principal and 
get his okay, I'll finish the assignment!</font>

102
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:23,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Splendid work, Tobari!</font>

103
00:06:23,150 --> 00:06:26,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You did it! You're the first one!</font>

104
00:06:26,780 --> 00:06:29,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm mad that you beat me to it.</font>

105
00:06:29,620 --> 00:06:31,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, congratulations.</font>

106
00:06:31,410 --> 00:06:34,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks. How are you all doing?</font>

107
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:40,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm giving lessons every day for the 
beginner class to teach them to write.</font>

108
00:06:40,470 --> 00:06:43,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My story's over 20,000 characters now.</font>

109
00:06:44,520 --> 00:06:46,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You sure did work hard, Ohgami.</font>

110
00:06:46,770 --> 00:06:48,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you're done now?</font>

111
00:06:48,290 --> 00:06:52,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, the plot's gotten too big!</font>

112
00:06:52,840 --> 00:06:53,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

113
00:06:53,670 --> 00:06:56,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The cast has taken on a mind of their own,</font>

114
00:06:56,390 --> 00:06:58,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with no ending in sight 
after 20,000 characters!</font>

115
00:06:58,850 --> 00:07:01,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know when I'll ever finish!</font>

116
00:07:01,170 --> 00:07:03,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. That sounds rough.</font>

117
00:07:04,140 --> 00:07:05,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about you, Kyoka?</font>

118
00:07:07,310 --> 00:07:10,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm ashamed to say 
that I've made no progress.</font>

119
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:13,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. Want me to help?</font>

120
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:15,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, that won't be necessary.</font>

121
00:07:15,860 --> 00:07:17,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is my assignment.</font>

122
00:07:18,220 --> 00:07:21,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll see through it all by myself.</font>

123
00:07:21,580 --> 00:07:22,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got it.</font>

124
00:07:22,930 --> 00:07:25,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, let us know if you need anything.</font>

125
00:07:25,300 --> 00:07:26,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're here to help.</font>

126
00:07:27,530 --> 00:07:30,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for your concern.</font>

127
00:07:32,200 --> 00:07:34,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<font size="18"><font face="Arial"><font color="#fbfeff">Feb. 7th (Fri.)
Class Duty: Minazuki</font></font></font></font>

128
00:07:34,670 --> 00:07:35,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've finished!</font>

129
00:07:36,160 --> 00:07:37,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A novella with a minimum of 20,000</font>

130
00:07:37,980 --> 00:07:39,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">characters and a cast of five or more!</font>

131
00:07:39,550 --> 00:07:41,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's complete!</font>

132
00:07:41,030 --> 00:07:44,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The final character count is 38,033!</font>

133
00:07:45,390 --> 00:07:47,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good job, Ohgami.</font>

134
00:07:47,710 --> 00:07:51,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I might enjoy 
coming up with stories.</font>

135
00:07:51,730 --> 00:07:53,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's great!</font>

136
00:07:53,220 --> 00:07:55,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's embarrassing to ask, 
but would you care to read it?</font>

137
00:07:55,870 --> 00:07:56,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure!</font>

138
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:58,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<font size="20"><font face="Arial"><font color="#f8f8f8">Feb. 14th (Fri.)
Class Duty: Usami</font></font></font></font>

139
00:07:58,830 --> 00:08:01,390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#978f89">{\an9}Signature Book</font>

140
00:07:58,830 --> 00:08:01,390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#978f89">{\an9}<font size="16">Sui Usami</font></font>

141
00:07:58,830 --> 00:08:00,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm done...</font>

142
00:08:00,870 --> 00:08:05,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I spent so much time teaching them 
to write, day in and day out.</font>

143
00:08:05,430 --> 00:08:07,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Some ran away.</font>

144
00:08:07,550 --> 00:08:09,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Some were scared.</font>

145
00:08:09,300 --> 00:08:11,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Some set up traps for me.</font>

146
00:08:11,550 --> 00:08:12,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a royal pain.</font>

147
00:08:13,500 --> 00:08:15,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. You worked really hard.</font>

148
00:08:16,700 --> 00:08:17,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

149
00:08:17,690 --> 00:08:20,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kyoka, how's your assignment going?</font>

150
00:08:22,180 --> 00:08:28,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, if there's anything I can do,
please don't hesitate to ask for help!</font>

151
00:08:29,320 --> 00:08:31,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're too kind.</font>

152
00:08:31,300 --> 00:08:36,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That said, it's my assignment, 
so I'll do my best by myself.</font>

153
00:08:38,870 --> 00:08:41,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I learned the hard way!</font>

154
00:08:42,330 --> 00:08:45,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you don't put your feelings into words,
they won't get through!</font>

155
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:51,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So perhaps I may be acting out of line...</font>

156
00:08:51,490 --> 00:08:55,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if you need help, 
feel free to ask at any time!</font>

157
00:08:59,250 --> 00:09:02,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I'll ask when the time is right.</font>

158
00:09:05,660 --> 00:09:06,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kyoka!</font>

159
00:09:06,730 --> 00:09:09,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me what part 
you're having trouble with!</font>

160
00:09:09,420 --> 00:09:11,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll help you out!</font>

161
00:09:11,940 --> 00:09:13,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for offering.</font>

162
00:09:13,810 --> 00:09:18,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, this assignment is 
for me to solve, so I'll be just fine.</font>

163
00:09:19,530 --> 00:09:20,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can tell it's fake.</font>

164
00:09:21,410 --> 00:09:22,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

165
00:09:22,710 --> 00:09:26,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never liked the way you smile.</font>

166
00:09:26,370 --> 00:09:30,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It reminds me of the person I love, 
forcing a smile on her face.</font>

167
00:09:32,670 --> 00:09:38,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I simply hold pride 
in always staying positive.</font>

168
00:09:38,210 --> 00:09:42,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forced as it may be, it is my wish 
to challenge myself and overcome this.</font>

169
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:44,310
