<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A tour of the school.</font>

234
00:13:06,810 --> 00:13:10,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After the tour, they handed out 
a hiragana worksheet.</font>

235
00:13:10,340 --> 00:13:12,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then we introduced ourselves.</font>

236
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:17,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The beginner class starts by learning 
about writing and speaking.</font>

237
00:13:17,560 --> 00:13:19,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

238
00:13:19,350 --> 00:13:23,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kyoka, do you remember 
our first introductions?</font>

239
00:13:23,100 --> 00:13:25,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our first introductions?</font>

240
00:13:25,390 --> 00:13:29,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your name and the reason 
you want to be human.</font>

241
00:13:31,910 --> 00:13:38,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to become human to repay 
the kindness a human showed me.</font>

242
00:13:38,510 --> 00:13:44,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I also want to 
help the people around me.</font>

243
00:13:45,220 --> 00:13:46,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And so...</font>

244
00:13:46,420 --> 00:13:50,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kyoka, I'm sorry about what I said!</font>

245
00:13:50,370 --> 00:13:51,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

246
00:13:51,430 --> 00:13:56,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wasn't thinking about how you felt, 
wanting to do your best.</font>

247
00:13:56,620 --> 00:13:59,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just wanted to help.</font>

248
00:13:59,400 --> 00:14:01,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For my own satisfaction.</font>

249
00:14:01,570 --> 00:14:03,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Usami...</font>

250
00:14:03,750 --> 00:14:05,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, don't say that.</font>

251
00:14:05,820 --> 00:14:07,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not at fault here, Usami.</font>

252
00:14:09,490 --> 00:14:11,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should also...</font>

253
00:14:11,660 --> 00:14:13,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well...</font>

254
00:14:13,200 --> 00:14:14,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Minazuki.</font>

255
00:14:15,740 --> 00:14:16,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know...</font>

256
00:14:17,940 --> 00:14:21,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't do anything 
without depending on others.</font>

257
00:14:22,770 --> 00:14:27,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even for stuff I was asked to do, 
I often find I can't do it alone.</font>

258
00:14:28,330 --> 00:14:34,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it's a really important skill to 
be able to ask others when that happens.</font>

259
00:14:35,820 --> 00:14:39,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No human can survive all on their own.</font>

260
00:14:40,310 --> 00:14:44,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We bother those around us, 
as they bother us.</font>

261
00:14:44,570 --> 00:14:47,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Life is all about supporting 
each other in that way.</font>

262
00:14:50,310 --> 00:14:52,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it really all right?</font>

263
00:14:53,000 --> 00:15:00,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would it be all right for me to ask you 
for your precious time?</font>

264
00:15:01,290 --> 00:15:03,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I already said it was okay.</font>

265
00:15:03,760 --> 00:15:05,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine by me as well.</font>

266
00:15:05,590 --> 00:15:08,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah! You betcha!</font>

