00:15:08,840 --> 00:15:10,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone...</font>

268
00:15:10,520 --> 00:15:12,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, don't forget I'm here, too.</font>

269
00:15:14,810 --> 00:15:17,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That goes without saying, Mr. Hitoma!</font>

270
00:15:18,970 --> 00:15:23,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone, please lend me your assistance!</font>

271
00:15:24,100 --> 00:15:25,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

