<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isaki, does that ring a bell?</font>

332
00:17:07,620 --> 00:17:09,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I-Isaki?!</font>

333
00:17:09,630 --> 00:17:11,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-If you ask Isaki...</font>

334
00:17:11,460 --> 00:17:13,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well...</font>

335
00:17:15,140 --> 00:17:16,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Hitoma...</font>

336
00:17:16,990 --> 00:17:17,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

337
00:17:17,860 --> 00:17:20,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, did you and Isaki...</font>

338
00:17:20,570 --> 00:17:23,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know what you're thinking, 
but you're wrong!</font>

339
00:17:23,230 --> 00:17:24,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At least I think so!</font>

340
00:17:25,500 --> 00:17:28,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! You say something, too, Ohgami!</font>

341
00:17:28,800 --> 00:17:31,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isaki can't talk here...</font>

342
00:17:31,100 --> 00:17:32,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why not?!</font>

343
00:17:32,630 --> 00:17:36,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is Isaki we're 
talking about, not Isaki!</font>

344
00:17:36,670 --> 00:17:39,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isaki can't just go blabbing about it!</font>

345
00:17:39,160 --> 00:17:40,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this all about?</font>

346
00:17:40,850 --> 00:17:46,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, the novel that Isaki wrote 
for her graduation assignment...</font>

347
00:17:47,790 --> 00:17:50,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isaki can't say any more!</font>

348
00:17:51,160 --> 00:17:56,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isaki will go back to being 
Isaki tomorrow, so ask Isaki then!</font>

349
00:18:00,390 --> 00:18:04,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In my novel, it took place 
under the cherry tree.</font>

350
00:18:04,990 --> 00:18:06,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's all look for it!</font>

351
00:18:06,890 --> 00:18:08,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Time to hunt for treasure!</font>

352
00:18:08,350 --> 00:18:09,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, wait, everyone!</font>

353
00:18:09,900 --> 00:18:12,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Make sure you don't go 
beyond the cherry tree!</font>

354
00:18:24,100 --> 00:18:25,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Minazuki!</font>

355
00:18:25,370 --> 00:18:27,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see it. Up there!</font>

356
00:18:30,390 --> 00:18:31,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A treasure chest.</font>

357
00:18:31,880 --> 00:18:34,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It sure is high up.</font>

358
00:18:34,700 --> 00:18:37,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will it come falling down if we shake it?</font>

359
00:18:37,380 --> 00:18:38,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me give it a try.</font>

360
00:18:38,800 --> 00:18:39,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There!</font>

361
00:18:41,910 --> 00:18:43,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You suck.</font>

362
00:18:43,530 --> 00:18:45,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about we throw something at it?</font>

363
00:18:45,790 --> 00:18:47,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like a game of darts or target practice.</font>

364
00:18:47,890 --> 00:18:49,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's an excellent suggestion!</font>

365
00:18:50,930 --> 00:18:52,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me.</font>

366
00:18:52,980 --> 00:18:59,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could I possibly impose upon you to use 
that feather to knock the chest down?</font>

367
00:19:00,520 --> 00:19:01,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's no good!</font>

368
00:19:01,280 --> 00:19:03,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How could you?!</font>

369
00:19:04,490 --> 00:19:06,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No need to be so formal.</font>

370
00:19:06,810 --> 00:19:09,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ask a little more casually, 
and I'd be happy to.</font>

371
00:19:10,510 --> 00:19:11,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Casually?</font>

372
00:19:12,180 --> 00:19:15,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You sounded so pompous, 
it caught me off guard.</font>

373
00:19:15,790 --> 00:19:17,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pompous?</font>

374
00:19:18,770 --> 00:19:21,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tobari, can you grab that box for me?</font>

375
00:19:22,030 --> 00:19:22,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure thing!</font>

376
00:19:24,220 --> 00:19:26,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, here goes nothing.</font>

377
00:19:26,020 --> 00:19:26,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

378
00:19:28,970 --> 00:19:29,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There!</font>

379
00:19:30,230 --> 00:19:31,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You did it!</font>

380
00:19:38,370 --> 00:19:39,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no! The barrier!</font>

381
00:19:40,110 --> 00:19:42,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Minazuki, stop!</font>

382
00:19:47,640 --> 00:19:48,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Hitoma!</font>

383
00:19:48,990 --> 00:19:50,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you hurt?</font>

384
00:19:51,190 --> 00:19:52,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I'm fine.</font>

385
00:19:53,870 --> 00:19:55,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The box is safe as well!</font>

386
00:20:02,410 --> 00:20:04,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you so much.</font>

387
00:20:09,590 --> 00:20:12,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Congratulations!</font>

388
00:20:14,190 --> 00:20:19,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like everyone in the advanced class 
has finished their final assignments!</font>

389
00:20:26,300 --> 00:20:30,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Principal, my apologies 
for taking so long.</font>

390
00:20:30,860 --> 00:20:34,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would not have been able to 
complete this assignment alone.</font>

391
00:20:35,390 --> 00:20:40,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, I was able to see it through 
thanks to my wonderful friends.</font>

392
00:20:41,350 --> 00:20:42,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As such...</font>

393
00:20:43,350 --> 00:20:49,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please distribute my points equally among 
the four of us in our class.</font>

394
00:20:50,050 --> 00:20:51,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once again...</font>

395
00:20:53,540 --> 00:20:55,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Congratulations!</font>

396
00:20:57,960 --> 00:21:02,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With this, all of your graduation 
assignments have been submitted.</font>

397
00:21:03,390 --> 00:21:09,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And we have decided which students meet 
the requirements to graduate.</font>

398
00:21:11,320 --> 00:21:14,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We will have one student 
graduating this year.</font>

399
00:21:14,220 --> 00:21:18,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She has no violations on record, 
and has consistently acquired points.</font>

400
00:21:18,560 --> 00:21:25,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A student with the clear academic 
and social skills to survive among humans.</font>

401
00:21:25,300 --> 00:21:29,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, she could never muster 
the courage to rely on others.</font>

402
00:21:30,140 --> 00:21:34,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A student adamant on doing 
everything by herself.</font>

403
00:21:35,910 --> 00:21:40,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But by relying on others 
for her graduation assignment,</font>

404
00:21:40,600 --> 00:21:44,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">she finally learned to become a bother.</font>

405
00:21:45,400 --> 00:21:50,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For these reasons stated, 
the one graduating will be...</font>

406
00:21:52,890 --> 00:21:54,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kyoka Minazuki.</font>

407
00:21:55,080 --> 00:21:56,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the one.</font>

408
00:22:00,070 --> 00:22:01,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much!</font>

409
